Package: ergMargins
Type: Package
Title: Package to calculate marginal effects and conduct mediation/moderation analyses in ERGM.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Scott Duxbury, The Ohio State University.
Maintainer: Scott Duxbury <duxbury.5@osu.edu>
Description: Implements a series of tests in ERGM, including calculation of marginal effects, 
    diagnostic tests for multicollinearity,
    mediation analysis, and tests of significance for interactions.
